OL,3,CCouncil calls on Government to provide
OL,4,Caid to victims of New Years flooding
OL,6,FStockport council has called on the
OL,7,FGovernment's Department of
OL,8,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,9,F(DEFRA) to provide aid emergency aid
OL,10,Ffunding to help people who were forced
OL,11,Fto evacuate their apartment complex
OL,12,Fdue to heavy flooding.
OL,14,FMore than 400 people were forced from
OL,15,FMeadow Mill in Stockport, Greater
OL,16,FManchester, after the car park and
OL,17,Fground floor were submerged in water
OL,18,Ffollowing heavy rainfall on 31
OL,19,FDecember.
