OL,3,CCouncil calls on Government to provide
OL,4,Caid to victims of New Years flooding
OL,6,FWhile some residents have been able to
OL,7,Freturn to their homes, many will have
OL,8,Fto remain in temporary accommodation
OL,9,Ffor the next few months as repair
OL,10,Fworks take place.
OL,12,FIn an open letter to Emma Hardy MP,
OL,13,Fwho leads DEFRA, the council called on
OL,14,Fher to release emergency funding to
OL,15,Fhelp displaced residents.
