OL,3,CCouncil calls on Government to provide
OL,4,Caid to victims of New Years flooding
OL,6,FCouncillor Jilly Julian wrote in the
OL,7,Fletter: "A significant amount of
OL,8,Fdamage was caused by the flooding -
OL,9,Fbusinesses have closed and hundreds of
OL,10,Fresidents have had to leave their
OL,11,Fhomes, some of which won't be
OL,12,Fhabitable again for months."
OL,14,FCllr Julian called on DEFRA to active
OL,15,Fthe Flood Recovery Framework, which
OL,16,Fwould entitle the council to more
OL,17,Ffunding for supporting the people of
OL,18,FMeadow Mill.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
