OL,3,CCouncil calls on Government to provide
OL,4,Caid to victims of New Years flooding
OL,6,FShe said: "I understand that whether
OL,7,Fthe Flood Recovery Framework is
OL,8,Factivated... is a ministerial decision
OL,9,F` one that was taken in 2019, 2023,
OL,10,Fand in 2024.
OL,12,F"Without that decision, and the
OL,13,Ffunding it makes available, councils
OL,14,Fsimply cannot afford to provide badly
OL,15,Fneeded relief.
OL,17,F"However, despite the widespread
OL,18,Fdevastation across our borough, we
OL,19,Fhave received no correspondence from
OL,20,Fcentral Government as to why this
OL,21,Fsupport has not been triggered."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
