OL,3,CCouncil calls on Government to provide
OL,4,Caid to victims of New Years flooding
OL,6,FIn the letter, Cllr Julian criticised
OL,7,Fthe Government's handling of the
OL,8,Fflooding on New Years Day, and said
OL,9,Fthe framework should have been
OL,10,Factivated as soon as the scale of the
OL,11,Fdisplacement was made clear.
OL,13,FShe said: "I'm keen to know why you
OL,14,Fchose not to activate the Flood
OL,15,FRecovery Framework following
OL,17,Fthe 1st of January 2025, and provide
OL,18,Fmuch needed crisis relief in an
OL,19,Falready challenging financial climate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
