OL,3,CCouncil calls on Government to provide
OL,4,Caid to victims of New Years flooding
OL,6,FTen days after the floods hit,
OL,7,FStockport insurance provider AXA
OL,8,Fagreed to provide accommodation for
OL,9,Fthose unable to return to their
OL,10,Fapartments in the mill.
OL,12,FDEFRA has been approached for comment.
